Articles.Content:
Over the course of about one Kerbal year this probes vertical orbit will allow it to scan all of the kethane deposits on Kerbin, So far the most useful thing I've launched in a while.

Titan rocket launch stage: http://imgur.com/HRkj2P8

Titan Orbital stage: http://imgur.com/QZpYbbe

Krol fully deployed: http://imgur.com/4vMFdUp

Woot, launching a vehicle on this kind of course saved me a lot of time.
